
1  Nejoki Elisha toning'o ororei lo Laitoriani: Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ore taisere tena rishata, nemiri entemet empirbil entapa napuyiapui te shekeli nabo, ore mpirbili are e shairi te shekeli nabo, te kishomi e Samaria. 
2  Ore ilo kitok le njore laa ninye apa eigarakino o laiguanani, nejoki ilo tung'ani le Nkai, “Amaa napaji tenaa kebol Olaitoriani ilusien e keper, keitabari ena bae?” Nejoki ilo tung'ani le Nkai ninye, “Ilo iyie adol too nkonyek inono, kake minos iyie.”

Eisika enjore e Siria


3  Netii apa iltung'ana oong'uan oata enkeeya oo lbolot ootii embata e kishomi; nejokino ninche maate, “Kainyoo iyiook pee kitoni tene o matuata? 
4  Tenikijo iyiook matijing atua enkanasa; netii olameyu atua enkanasa, naa eikipuo aaye teine. Naa tenekitoni tene nikiye ake sii. Maape naa taata ilng'oborri loo ltung'ana le Siria. Tenetapala ninche iyiook, nikinchu, naa tenetaara iyiook matuata, nikiye naa.” 
5  Nedumunye ninche, pee emirimiru enteipa aapuo ilng'oborri le Siria, kake ore ake pee ebau emanaroto oo lng'oborri loo ltung'ana le Siria, ng'ura, metii hoo toki ine. 
6  Amu eishoo apa Olaitoriani iltung'ana le Siria metoning'o oltoilo loo ngarrin oo mbartan, o loo mbartan, o ltoilo le njore kitok, neaku etiaakinote maate, “Ng'ura, eipotuo olaiguanani loo Siraeli, aiger o laiguanani le Hiti, o laiguanani le Misiri meetu aarare iyiook.” 
7  Neisik ninche ina teipa aailanyisho, neing'uaa ilng'oborri lenye, o mbartan enye, o sirkon lenye, neing'uaa ilng'oborri etiu anaa duoo ake. Neilanyisho aaitajeu enkishui enye. 
8  Ore ake pee epuonu kulo tung'ana le nkeeya oo lbolot emanaroto oo lng'oborri, nejing ninche atua olng'obor, nedaa neokisho, neya ninche enkosholai o sahabu o nkilani nepuo aaisudoo. Neitoki aapuonu nejing likae ng'obor, neya ntokitin tiatua ilo ng'obor, nepuo aaisudoo.


9  Neitoki aajokino maate, “Mme embae sidai iyiook kiaasita. Ore ena olong naa enkolong oo lomon supati. Tenikigira iyiook o mekenyu, naa kebaiki iyiook enkitamioto. Ore naa taata, wootu maape aajoki enkaji o laiguanani.” 
10  Nepuonu ninche aaipot ilarripok loo nchomito e nkanasa, neliki ninche aajoki, “Kishomo iyiook ilng'oborri loo ltung'ana le Siria, ng'ura medoli nemening'i hoo oltung'ani obo teine, meteleku ake mbartan naaena o sirkon ooena, netiu lelo ng'oborri anaa apake.” 
11  Neipotisho lelo arripok le kishomi, nelimuni ina bae tiatua enkaji o laiguanani. 
12  Nedumunye olaiguanani kewarie, nejoki isinkan lenyena, “Kaliki nanu intae ina naitobira iltung'ana le Siria tialo iyiook. Eyiolo ninche aajo eikisumash; neaku eipang'a ninche too lng'oborri aapuo aaisudori te nkop naisiaja, ejo, ‘Teneipangu ninche te nkanasa, nikiya iyiook ninche, eishu meshomo eyararoto nikijing atua enkanasa.’ ” 
13  Nejo obo loo sinkan lenyena, “Nchoo ilkuti tung'ana eya nena bartan imiet apa naatelekutua, amu idolitata aajo, ore kulo ootelekutua netiu ake anaa ilo orora pooki le Israel oidaa. Mairriwuai ninche meshomo aadol.” 
14  Neyau ninche iltung'ana oare oo kedito mbartan, neirriwaa olaiguanani ninche meshomo aasujaa enjore e Siria, nejoki, “Enchom entodol.” 
15  Nepuo ninche aasujaa ninche ometabaiki olkeju le Yordan; naa ng'ura, ore te nkoitoi pooki, naa mpurdat oo nkilani o ntokitin naaiturraitie iltung'ana le Siria te nkisarrisar. Nerrinyunye lelo tung'ana ooirriwayioki, neliki olaiguanani.


16  Neipang iltung'ana nepuo aar lelo ng'oborri loo ltung'ana le Siria. Neaku ore empirbil entapa napuyiapui nemiri te shekeli nabo, ore mpirbili are e shairi nemiri te shekeli nabo te risioroto o rorei lo Laitoriani. 
17  Netegelua apa olaiguanani olkitok le njore laa ninye eisilig, metaa olarriponi le kishomi. Neitunyoo iltung'ana ninye te kishomi o metua, anaa enatejo oltung'ani le Nkai, ina kata pee elotu olaiguanani aduaare ninye. 
18  Amu ore ina kata pee ejoki oltung'ani le Nkai olaiguanani, “Kemirieki mpirbili are e shairi te shekeli nabo, neinosieki empirbil e ntapa napuyiapui shekeli nabo, taisere, tena rishata, te kishomi e Samaria.” 
19  Etawalikia apa ilo kitok le njore oltung'ani le Nkai ajoki, “Amaa napaji tenaa kebol Olaitoriani ilusien te keper, keitabari ena bae?” Nejoki ilo tung'ani le Nkai ninye, “Ilo iyie adol too nkonyek inono, kake miinos iyie ina daa.” 
20  Neaku neijia ake etotiwuo te ninye, amu eitunyoitie iltung'ana ninye te kishomi neye.

